{"type": "article", "id": 16476, "title": "Cabinet & Desk", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-23T06:40:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060003432ArSflZQXV1xEqzC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t英国设计师 Benjamin Ashton 设计了这张桌子和柜子，运用了非常明亮的色彩和剪纸元素。天蓝色、浅粉色、黄色搭配米色的木质家具，给人清爽阳光的感受。储物柜上的竖条镂空元素配合不同的颜色，让三层空间都显得不同。相应的，桌子的挡板上则用了一些圆点，也是挂备忘录的好地方。它们都有一种让人一起玩的冲动。<a href=\"http://www.benjamin-ashton.com/index-projects/#/cabinet-desk/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143728gcrfBG68VFAhKqkw.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"476\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.79333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143729r9bwXOTYdD8iLMFC.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"558\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.93\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143729esTENjaI1zUZfxqg.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"402\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261437302k8OTaKWNPBp4wLS.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"377\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.62833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}